    {
      "id": "1ad4750c-f3ba-8052-b878-ea103b5185b6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Prior performance was established to be the primary predictor, with the remaining feature sets loosing significance after incorporating data from this source. Moreover, the authors established that good predictions could be achieved as early as week 6, but with uncertainty decreasing at later stages of prediction. \n",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1ad4750c-f3ba-8052-b878-ea103b5185b6",
